OL,3,CHigh prices sparked by Iran war could
OL,4,Clinger for years, EU official warns
OL,6,FThe energy crisis and subsequent price
OL,7,Fhikes caused by the Iran war could
OL,8,Flast for months, if not years,
OL,9,Faccording to the European Union's top
OL,10,Fenergy official.
OL,12,FEU Energy Commissioner Dan Jorgensen
OL,13,Fsaid on Wednesday this is "not a short-
OL,14,Fterm" issue as he spoke to reporters
OL,15,Fat a press conference.
OL,17,F"This is a crisis that is probably as
OL,18,Fserious as the 1973 and the 2022
OL,19,Fcrises combined," he said.
