OL,3,CHigh prices sparked by Iran war could
OL,4,Clinger for years, EU official warns
OL,6,FJorgensen added the war is costing
OL,7,FEurope around 500 million euros
OL,8,F(#434m) each day and that "we are
OL,9,Flooking into some very difficult
OL,10,Fmonths, or maybe even years" ahead.
OL,12,F"Even in a best-case scenario, it's
OL,13,Fstill bad," he told reporters.
