OL,3,CHigh prices sparked by Iran war could
OL,4,Clinger for years, EU official warns
OL,6,FThe comments come as UK inflation hit
OL,7,F3.3% in March, mainly thanks to higher
OL,8,Ffuel prices triggered by the conflict,
OL,9,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,10,FStatistics (ONS).
OL,12,FThe higher cost of motor fuel was the
OL,13,Fmain driver of the acceleration in
OL,14,Finflation, after it increased by 8.7%
OL,15,Fmonth-on-month.
OL,17,FIt is the largest increase since June
OL,18,F2022, when fuel prices spiked shortly
OL,19,Fafter Russia's invasion of Ukraine.
