PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776885106
OL,3,CHigh prices sparked by Iran war could
OL,4,Clinger for years, EU official warns
OL,6,FThe rate of inflation is up from 3% in
OL,7,FFebruary, and the figures are the
OL,8,Ffirst to be released since the US and
OL,9,FIsrael attacked Iran on February 28.
OL,11,FThe March rate is the highest since
OL,12,FDecember.
OL,14,FResponding to the figures, Chancellor
OL,15,FRachel Reeves said: "This is not our
OL,16,Fwar, but it is pushing up bills for
OL,17,Ffamilies and businesses. That's why
OL,18,Fit's my number one priority to keep
OL,19,Fcosts down."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
