OL,3,CHigh prices sparked by Iran war could
OL,4,Clinger for years, EU official warns
OL,6,FShe pointed to cuts in energy bills
OL,7,Fand the freezing of rail fares and
OL,8,Ffuel duty as examples of how the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment had helped the public.
